msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa unapatikana nje ya Marekani, tunapendekeza NOWPayments (ada ndogo "
"kabisa, moja kwa moja kwenye pochi yako). Ikiwa unapoendelea katika "
"Marekani, Stripe Crypto pia ni chaguo. Unaweza kuwezesha huduma nyingi na "
"kuruhusu wageni wako kuchagua!"

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Njia za Malipo Zilizowezeshwa"

msgid ""
"Select which payment options will appear in your widget. Your visitors can "
"choose their preferred method."
msgstr ""
"Chagua njia za malipo zitakazojulikana katika widget yako. Wageni wako "
"wanaweza kuchagua njia wanayotaka."

