"Display your wallet address so users can send crypto directly. Zero fees, "
"but requires users to already have crypto."
msgstr ""
"Onyesha anwani ya pochi yako ili watumiaji watumie crypto moja kwa moja. Ada"
" sifariji, lakini inahitaji watumiaji kuwa tayari na crypto."

