"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments inakuwezesha kugawia malipo ya kadi ya mkopo moja kwa moja "
"kwenye pochi yako ya crypto. Fedha inakwenda moja kwa moja kwenye pochi yako"
" – hakuna mhusika wa kati."

