msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Malipo ya Crypto ya Stripe (USDC) yanapatikana tu kwa biashara zinazotokana "
"na Marekani. Ikiwa uko nje ya Marekani, Stripe itakubali pekee malipo ya "
"kadi ya mkopo kwa salio lako la Stripe (sio moja kwa moja kwa crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa uko Marekani, unaweza kutumia Stripe kupewa crypto moja kwa moja. "
"Ikiwa uko nje, zingatia NOWPayments au CoinGate kwa matangazo ya crypto moja"
" kwa moja."

