msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Widget yenye nguvu, bure ya michango na malipo inayoamuru wageni wako "
"kukusaidia kupitia kadi ya mkopo au cryptocurrency (Quai). Hakuna ada za "
"kila mwezi, hakuna usajili wa watu wengine – kupunguza pochi yako na huduma "
"bure."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Baadhi ya kivinjari huzuia skripti za watu wengine kwa usiri. Proxy hii "
"inapakia skripti kupitia seva yako mwenyewe ili kupitisha kizuizi haya."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kusasisha URL za skripti hapa chini ikiwa URL za awali zitabadilika "
"au ikiwa unataka kutumia CDN tofauti."

